    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverioDAI2"/>, p. 114, n. <citedRange>103</citedRange>, fig. 59</bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>9.215</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>025900</citedRange></bibl>. 
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#beschi1970"/>, p. <citedRange>200</citedRange> and fig. 55 (discovery), p. <citedRange>204</citedRange> (date of the base)</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#belzic2022"/>, catalogue <citedRange>B.70</citedRange></bibl>.
                </p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64280"><name nymRef="#Θράσων">Θράσων</name> <persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64049"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Ἠρίνοος">Ἠρινόου</name></persName></persName>.
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Thrasôn fils d'Erinoos.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Thrason son of Erinoos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Thrason figlio di Erinoos.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>This is probably one of the oldest epitaphs with the genitive <foreign xml:lang="grc">-ου</foreign> in koine.</p>
	      <p>Beschi shows an archive photograph proving that the base was found in the same undefined tomb as <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr026800</ref> 
	          and the mourning half-figure n. 7 of his catalogue, although the latter matches none of the bases.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
